dict.string: STRALIAS="colorscheme solarized | set background=light"; VIMALIAS='vim -c "'$STRALIAS'"'; echo "alias vim='$VIMALIAS'" > .temp && source ~/.bashrc
STRALIAS="colorscheme solarized | set background=dark"; VIMALIAS='vim -c "'$STRALIAS'"'; echo "alias vim='$VIMALIAS'" > .temp && source ~/.bashrc
